Create a new user-level lens by cloning an existing lens's filter/scoring as the starting point.

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} when adjust_audience determined the current lens cannot be edited (e.g. it's the org default).

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} to update an existing lens — use leadbay_update_lens or leadbay_update_lens_filter.

{{include:headers/verification-required-if-write}}
